We’ll talk about the role of hand gestures, and the role of facial expressions, particularly

14
00:00:57,329 --> 00:01:00,440
because the face is good at communicating emotion.

15
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:05,210
We&#39;ll also talk about cross-cultural differences in nonverbal communication.

16
